<div style="margin: 0px;">

   <div id="widgets" class="banner">
 one central location to engage in conversations with your friends and friends of your friends and to organize all that information<br/>
  </div>
<div id="dashboard-content">


 
  <div id="whatis">
    <%= image_tag "whatis.png" %>
  </div>


  <div id="howto">
   <h2>
     How to use EngageVia?
    </h2>   

    <ol>
      <% bk_link = "javascript:location.href=' #{DOMAIN}posts/new?url='+encodeURIComponent(location.href)+';title='+encodeURIComponent(document.title)" %>
      <li>Drag this <%= link_to  "EngageVia bookmarklet", bk_link, :title => "EngageVia bookmarklet"  %> to your browser's bookmarks.
      <li>Click on it whenever you want to engage or simply visit <a title="EngageVia" href="http://www.engagevia.com/posts/new">EngageVia</a> </li>
      <li>Fill up the basic information about the topic of your choice and <br/>a conversation page is created. </li>
      <li>From that page, Invite only relevant friends from your address book. </li>
      <li>A link to the Conversation page is sent to them. </li>
      <li>Let your invitees invite relevant friends from their circle as well.</li>
      <li>All the invitees converge at one central location to engage in the conversation.   </li>
      <li>If you are a content publisher, copy the following javascript snippet to paste in your pages to facilitate private discussions</li>
    </ol>
      <div id="js_snippet">
        <% snippet = "<img src='http://www.engagevia.com/images/e2.png'>    <a href='http://www.engagevia.com/posts/new' onclick='window.open('http://www.engagevia.com/posts/new?noui&amp;jump=close&amp;url='+encodeURIComponent(location.href)+'&amp;title='+encodeURIComponent(document.title),'EngageVia','toolbar=no,width=800,height=600'); return false;'> Start a conversation on EngageVia</a>"        %>
        <%= text_area_tag 'snippet', snippet, :rows => 5, :cols => 120, :readonly => true %>
      </div>
 </div>

  <div id="signup">
 <%= button_to "Start a Conversation" , new_post_url %>
   No Membership required for checking it out. <br/> Start Now! <br/>
</div>
</div>

</div>

